OL,5,Cguard
OL,7,FWhen the guard repeated that the pass
OL,8,Fhad to be examined, Mr Anderson
OL,9,Fapproached them before saying "f***
OL,10,Fyou, I have a train to catch" and
OL,11,Fwalking out of the search post.
OL,13,FA complaint about the incident on
OL,14,FNovember 3 was upheld by Parliament's
OL,15,Fstandards commissioner.
