OL,5,Cguard
OL,7,FMr Anderson, who is the MP for
OL,8,FAshfield, initially appealed against
OL,9,Fthe finding to the Independent Expert
OL,10,FPanel, but his case was dismissed on
OL,11,Fthe basis that it "failed to raise any
OL,12,Fsubstantive grounds."
OL,14,FSince then, he has "accepted the
OL,15,Fcommissioner's finding that he had
OL,16,Fsworn at the complainant and that his
OL,17,Fbehaviour had been a breach of the
OL,18,Fbullying and harassment policy", the
OL,19,Fpanel said.
